message.body: Are you dating someone I want to know the details!
Lol honeybob asked me the same thing today
Haha. The people need to know!
I see that! I havent really said anything to anyone... we've been dating for just over a month.
We went to this haunted forest last weekend and I was laughing so hard because I was so scared. It was terrifying. Lol
Hes 34, born and raised in herndon. He coaches football and basketball. Really laid back which is a nice contrast to my craziness.
That's awesome! What's his name??
Haunted house sounds like soooo much fun!
I've been to a few of those they are terrifying!
So fun.
That's really cool though sounds like you guys are doing fun stuff.
you guys are coming down for Thanksgiving right
Yeah! We are. Hunter gets to meet the whole lot.
Oh man.
Mom just told me about Emma.
I want to throttle her
I know :( she is getting into a weird stage
I just talked to her and told her she has to call me once a week and come visit so I can keep tabs on her/
Shes going to rebel
Yup.
